Philippines Not in Favor of Speculative Inflows, Reviews NDFs

-- B y   M a x   E s t a y o
-- 
2011-09-30T03:22:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/philippines-not-in-favor-of-speculative-inflows-reviews-ndfs.html
The Philippine central bank is
monitoring inflows as it reviews the policy on non-deliverable
currency forwards or NDFs, Governor Amando Tetangco said in a
government economic briefing in  Manila . “We don’t favor inflows
that are speculative in nature,” Tetangco said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Max Estayo in Manila at 
 mestayo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
